OL,5,G1000 Car Pound Cops: Give Me My Car...
OL,6,     F...Back! Specialist car recovery
OL,7,     Fcompanies help local governments
OL,8,     Fand businesses take care of
OL,9,     Fillegal or dangerous vehicles by
OL,10,     Fgetting them off the road.
OL,11,G1100 Traffic Cops
OL,12,     FDerbyshire's police and other
OL,13,     Femergency services are called to
OL,14,     Fover 1600 crashes each year. In
OL,15,     Fthis episode, cops deal with
OL,16,     Fcrashes and distracted drivers
OL,17,     Fputting lives on the line.
