OL,5,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FAround 3000 people a year are
OL,7,     Fkilled or seriously injured
OL,8,     Fbecause of drink driving. In this
OL,9,     Fepisode, officers launch a drink
OL,10,     Fand drug driving crackdown and
OL,11,     Fmake about 200 arrests.
OL,12,G1300 Traffic Cops: Over the Limit
OL,13,     FCops clamp down on young drivers
OL,14,     Fand repeat offenders losing
OL,15,     Fcontrol while drink driving,
OL,16,     Fputting lives in danger, including
OL,17,     Fa suspected drink driver speeding
OL,18,     Fat 100mph.
