OL,5,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FKev and Pete pursue a car into a
OL,7,     Ffarmer's field, Jacko takes part
OL,8,     Fin a major heroin bust, and rookie
OL,9,     Fpolice dog Elsa chases a runaway
OL,10,     Fburglar through the streets of
OL,11,     FMiddlesbrough.
OL,12,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FInterceptor Paul 'the mustard'
OL,14,     FFaulkner has a close shave with a
OL,15,     Fstolen vehicle, Liam Sewell has a
OL,16,     Ffront row seat in a pirouetting
OL,17,     Fpursuit and Spike unearths a
OL,18,     Fbumper crop.
