OL,5,G1800 Home and Away
OL,6,     FAbigail works to persuade
OL,7,     FMackenzie. Richie's day goes from
OL,8,     Fbad to worse. Alf's unable to
OL,9,     Fenjoy the win.
OL,10,G1830 Home and Away
OL,11,     FSonny's caught in a lie. Roo baits
OL,12,     FAlf for the truth. Mackenzie makes
OL,13,     Fa big decision.
OL,14,G1900 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,15,     FDuring a packed shift, a
OL,16,     F53-year-old chef suffers chest
OL,17,     Fpains, an 84-year-old has had a
OL,18,     Ffall on an escalator, and a
OL,19,     Ffarmer's been crushed by a bull
OL,20,     Ffrom his herd.
