OL,5,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FCritical care teams race to save
OL,7,     Flives as a 61-year-old is injured
OL,8,     Fin a motorcycle crash, a new mum
OL,9,     Fhaemorrhages days after giving
OL,10,     Fbirth, and a 12-year-old suffers
OL,11,     Fsevere leg injuries.
OL,12,G2300 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,13,     FBen from Lewisham Council's Rogue
OL,14,     FLandlord Unit has just 24 hours to
OL,15,     Frehouse a single mother and her
OL,16,     Fchild or they will end up on the
OL,17,     Fstreets.
OL,18,G0000 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,19,     FMargaret tries to get the #20,000
OL,20,     Fshe is owed from a letting agent,
OL,21,     FStavros and Emily try to get their
OL,22,     Fhouse back from squatters.
